imdb.plot outline: Liah Yoo has quickly become one of the top international beauty vloggers. Based in Seoul, South Korea, Liah's holistic approach to skincare and beauty has earned her much praise and recognition as a leading industry expert. Liah served on the panel of the Korean beauty reality show "Get It Beauty" and has been nominated as the "15 Beauty YouTubers to Watch" by Teen Vogue.
imdb.title: Liah Yoo
plot: _Liah Yoo_ (qv) has quickly become one of the top international beauty vloggers. Based in Seoul, South Korea, Liah's holistic approach to skincare and beauty has earned her much praise and recognition as a leading industry expert. Liah served on the panel of the Korean beauty reality show "Get It Beauty" and has been nominated as the "15 Beauty YouTubers to Watch" by Teen Vogue.
